    "body": "In Rust everything is an expression, so you can just use:\n\n``` rust\nlet x = if condition { trueExpression } else { falseExpression };\n```\n\nRust originally had this, but it was removed in #1698. There's a small amount recent discussion on that issue about adding it back.\n",
